FuncDef: This command displays services using the range of egress labels.

ParaDef.Info: Specifies the starting egress label value for which to display services using the label range. If only egress-label1 is specified, services only using egress-label1 are displayed. Values-0, 2049 to 131071.
Specifies the ending egress label value for which to display services using the label range. Values-2049 to 131071. ParamDefault: Default- The egress-label1 value
